quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  38,43,"Wawahabna lahu ahlahu wamithlahummaAAahum rahmatan minna wathikrali-olee al-albab"
  38,44,"Wakhuth biyadika dighthan fadribbihi wala tahnath inna wajadnahu sabiranniAAma alAAabdu innahu awwab"
  38,45,"Wathkur AAibadanaibraheema wa-ishaqa wayaAAqooba olee al-aydee wal-absar"
  38,46,"Inna akhlasnahum bikhalisatinthikra addar"
  38,47,"Wa-innahum AAindana lamina almustafaynaal-akhyar"
  38,48,"Wathkur ismaAAeelawa-ilyasaAAa watha alkifli wakullun mina al-akhyar"
  38,49,"Hatha thikrun wa-innalilmuttaqeena lahusna maab"
  38,50,"Jannati AAadnin mufattahatanlahumu al-abwab"
  38,51,"Muttaki-eena feeha yadAAoona feehabifakihatin katheeratin washarab"
  38,52,"WaAAindahum qasiratu attarfiatrab"
  38,53,"Hatha ma tooAAadoona liyawmialhisab"
  38,54,"Inna hatha larizquna malahu min nafad"
  38,55,"Hatha wa-inna littagheenalasharra maab"
  38,56,"Jahannama yaslawnaha fabi/saalmihad"
  38,57,"Hatha falyathooqoohu hameemunwaghassaq"
  38,58,"Waakharu min shaklihi azwaj"
  38,59,"Hatha fawjun muqtahimunmaAAakum la marhaban bihim innahum saloo annar"
  38,60,"Qaloo bal antum la marhabanbikum antum qaddamtumoohu lana fabi/sa alqarar"
  38,61,"Qaloo rabbana man qaddama lanahatha fazidhu AAathaban diAAfan fee annar"
